'''AMDGPU''' is a family of open source graphics drivers for newer AMD/ATI Radeon graphics cards.

If the card in question is not found in the [[#Feature support|Feature support]] section below check the [[radeon]] article; it contains instructions for older open source AMD/ATI Radeon graphic card drivers.

== Installation ==

=== Prerequisites ===

==== Hardware detection ====

To choose the right driver, first detect the graphics card. Use {{c|[[Hardware detection#lspci|lspci]]}} for this task:

{{RootCmd|lspci {{!}} grep -i VGA}}

